{"tid":1277540,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"出糧戶口大優惠","createTime":"2019-07-02T08:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T10:40:04.000Z","uid":92170,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"75bf0c51447207c528f3a58d65cbe596cb086c50","tid":1277540,"uid":92170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:11:27.000Z","msg":"各大銀行最新出糧戶口優惠資訊，緊有一間啱你！<br />\n<br />\n請注意，滙豐及恆生提款機通用，即滙豐可於恆生提款機提款，反之亦可！<br />\n其他銀行提款機亦通用（不包括滙豐及恆生），即Citibank客戶可於渣打銀行提款機提款，但設最低提款要求，視乎銀行規定，每次最低提款額為３００或５００港元。如Ａ銀行客戶到Ｂ銀行提款機提款，Ａ銀行需向Ｂ銀行付手續費（有指每次收費５港元），現時有關費用由銀行支付，Ａ銀行客戶不需付費。詳情請向銀行查詢。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐及渣打宣布，8月起撤消指定戶口低結餘收費，詳情請向銀行查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">火熱推介　Citibank</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n開立出糧戶口可享高達 135,000 飛行里數或HK$10,200現金回贈!<br />\n<br />\n於2019年4月1日至2019年6月30日(更新資料請向Citibank查詢)期間成功開立全新Citibank戶口，即可享以下迎新獎賞。<br />\n<br />\n出糧戶口迎新獎賞<br />\n<br />\n月薪(HK$)    現金回贈 (HK$) / Avios 里數*<br />\n&ge; $80,000    $1,200    15,000里數<br />\n&ge; $50,000    $1,000    13,000里數<br />\n&ge; $30,000    $800    10,000里數<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n精彩股票服務優惠<br />\n出糧戶口客戶可享每月無上限買入港股免佣優惠<br />\n成功存入港股╱美股及上海A股可享高達HK$3,000現金劵獎賞<br />\n股票戶口特色<br />\n豁免最低經紀佣金及永久豁免存倉費、存入費<br />\n永久豁免存入股票之服務費<br />\n豁免網上認購新股之服務費<br />\n及其他優惠<br />\n<br />\n請即登記:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.citibank.com.hk/chinese/banking/citibank-payroll-account.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.citibank.com.hk%2Fchinese%2Fbanking%2Fcitibank-payroll-account.htm&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=d4937efd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.citibank.com.hk/chinese/banking/citibank-payroll-account.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">巴絲熱選　渣打銀行</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n由2019年3月30日至2019年6月30日(更新資料請向Citibank查詢)，包括首尾兩天（「推廣期」） ，成功開立「渣打紅利出糧戶口」並透過「渣打紅利出糧戶口」使用本行自動轉賬出糧服務，可享以下精彩優惠：<br />\n<br />\n高達1.68%港元活期推廣儲蓄年利率長達6個月<br />\n高達 10,000 「亞洲萬里通」里數或高達HK$1,000現金回贈<br />\n客戶推薦優惠可享每位1,000「亞洲萬里通」里數或HK$100<br />\n及其他優惠<br />\n<br />\n請即登記:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sc.com/hk/zh/promotion/save/salary-bonuspack/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sc.com%2Fhk%2Fzh%2Fpromotion%2Fsave%2Fsalary-bonuspack%2F&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=11186847\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sc.com/hk/zh/promotion/save/salary-bonuspack/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">富貴精選　滙豐銀行</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n開立全新滙豐運籌理財戶口，不設低額結存服務費。維持全面理財總值平均值為港幣20萬元或以上以繼續享用滙豐運籌理財服務的額外服務及禮遇。<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n及其他優惠<br />\n<br />\n請即登記:<br />\n<a href=\"https://retailbank.hsbc.com.hk/weadvance/zh-hk/welcome-rewards/welcome/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fretailbank.hsbc.com.hk%2Fweadvance%2Fzh-hk%2Fwelcome-rewards%2Fwelcome%2F&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=9ef86af3\" target=\"_blank\">https://retailbank.hsbc.com.hk/weadvance/zh-hk/welcome-rewards/welcome/</a><br />\n聯絡滙豐：2233 3000<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">精彩人生　恆生銀行</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n由2019年4月1日至9月30日，轉用本行戶口為出糧戶口之合資格客戶1，於出糧期1內每月平均出糧金額2達HKD10,000並符合指定要求，可享高達$4,800 Cash Dollars！<br />\n<br />\n每月平均出糧金額    可享之Cash Dollars<br />\nHKD80,000或以上    $1,000<br />\nHKD50,000至HKD80,000以下    $800<br />\nHKD30,000至HKD50,000以下    $350<br />\nHKD10,000至HKD30,000以下    $100<br />\n<br />\n網上登記獎賞<br />\n於網上成功登記本推廣，可享<br />\n$100 Cash Dollars<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n及其他優惠<br />\n<br />\n登記熱線 2998 6018<br />\n<br />\n請即登記:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hangseng.com/cms/emkt/pmo/grp04/p06/chi/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hangseng.com%2Fcms%2Femkt%2Fpmo%2Fgrp04%2Fp06%2Fchi%2Findex.html&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=44e1956b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hangseng.com/cms/emkt/pmo/grp04/p06/chi/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">［頭盔］本文只供參考，所有優惠及資料以銀行公佈為準，請自行查詢。［／頭盔］<br />\n［頭盔］上文連結不涉客戶推薦優惠，歡迎轉發。［／頭盔］</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85103b75a80c4645e4dfd88221a7e8d8837d1e50","tid":1277540,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee498fa8c942319720e551ea57d539d55fd2454c","tid":1277540,"uid":55533,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錢就citi<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mrmiles.hk/citi-avios-priority-banking/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mrmiles.hk%2Fciti-avios-priority-banking%2F&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=d03644cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mrmiles.hk/citi-avios-priority-banking/</a><br />\n冇錢就大新<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mrmiles.hk/dahsing-banking/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mrmiles.hk%2Fdahsing-banking%2F&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=4e511263\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mrmiles.hk/dahsing-banking/</a>"},{"pid":"7287c2c4d9e01f66b47f3f17c5f2f8448ea33a3f","tid":1277540,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee498fa8c942319720e551ea57d539d55fd2454c","tid":1277540,"uid":55533,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no